<P><H1 align=center>BANKRUPTCY HISTORY – DC140</H1>
<P></P>
<P><FONT color=red><STRONG>NOTE: </STRONG>fields shown in 
red are mandatory and must be completed to proceed</FONT>            </P>
<P>If the applicant has previously been declared bankrupt, click on the ‘Yes’ 
radio button, which enables the ‘Add’ key</P>
<P><H3>Add: </H3>clicking on ‘Add’ leads to <A HREF="HELP_DC141.asp">Add / Edit 
Bankruptcy History (DC141)</A> where all details are taken. The details will then be 
shown in the main box – name, amount of debt, monthly repayment, date declared 
and date of discharge
<P></P>
<P><H3>Edit / Delete: </H3>to edit or delete a record, 
highlight it and click on the ‘Edit’ or ‘Delete’ button
<P></P>
<P><H3>OK: </H3>clicking on ‘OK’ leads to the next screen.
